title: Before You Start Dating Someone From TikTok, Listen To This Warning!
description:
We've all heard how specific TikTok's algorithm is, but is it too specific? Our Producer Keity thinks so and for good reason. It has to do with a few of the women she's dated in the past and a friend of hers. Let's just say you might want to think again before using this app for dating purposes.
